{"article_id":"pdvqstmxHU51E90C","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Obama 's Next Big Campaign :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Selling Health Care To The Public","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"President Obama often tells audiences","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that he has waged his last campaign .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"But that 's not exactly true .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"The White House is gearing up for a massive campaign this summer","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"that will cover all 50 states , plus Washington , D.C.","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"And the president 's legacy may hinge on whether it succeeds or fails .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"The Affordable Care Act , or `` Obamacare , '' has been through more life-and-death cliffhangers than a season finale of Homeland .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"After squeaker votes in Congress and a 5-4 ruling","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"upholding the law at the Supreme Court ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"now there 's another big hurdle :","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"getting uninsured people to buy health care","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"when it becomes available Oct. 1 .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"When Obama delivered the commencement address at Morehouse College this month ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"his advice to the graduates","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"- along with working hard and helping others -","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"was to sign up for health insurance this fall .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` We 've got to make sure","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"everybody has good health in this country , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"`` It 's not just good for you ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"it 's good for this country .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"So you 're going to have to spread the word to your fellow young people . ''","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"David Simas , deputy senior adviser to the president , works in a quintessential West Wing office","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"- a windowless basement room -","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"where he oversees one of the top projects on the Obama agenda :","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"implementing universal health coverage .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"In the first year , the administration hopes to sign up 7 million people across the country .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Simas says","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that will require TV ads , door knocking and lots of word of mouth .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"`` It is an on-the-ground effort , ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"he says .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"`` It is a social media effort .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"It is a paid media effort .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"It is an earned media effort .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"But [ it 's ] all leading to the same thing ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"which is that man or woman","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"sitting in their living room online ,","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"comparing different prices for different products","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"and deciding what works best for them . ''","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"The administration is developing an Expedia-style website ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"hoping to make the experience as customer-friendly as possible .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"But just getting people to that website is a huge task .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Last month , a Kaiser Family Foundation poll showed","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that 4 in 10 Americans do n't even know","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"the health care law is still on the books .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Nancy-Ann DeParle ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"who has worked on this issue for years","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"- until recently as Obama 's deputy chief of staff -","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"says","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that 's not a cause for concern .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` The truth is that people were n't paying attention until now , ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"she says .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` There 's so much else going on","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"even if we had wanted to start a campaign two years ago ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"it would n't have been very effective","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"because people were n't listening . ''","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"with the sign-up date approaching fast ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"the administration 's efforts have already stumbled .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Health and Human Services Secretary Kathleen Sebelius has repeatedly asked Congress for money","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"to implement Obamacare .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Republicans have repeatedly said no ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"while they vote to repeal the law .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Without the money","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"she wanted from Congress ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Sebelius tried to fundraise for an independent group","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"called Enroll America","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"that is focused on implementing Obamacare .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"When Republicans heard","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"that she was asking insurance companies and health care providers to donate millions of dollars ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"they cried foul .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Tennessee Sen. Lamar Alexander told Fox News :","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"`` Congress has said","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"we refuse to give you more money","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"to implement Obamacare ,","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"and she 's saying ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"'Well then ,","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"if you wo n't do it ,","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"I 'll go outside","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"and I will raise private money ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"use a private organization ,","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"and do it anyway . ' ``","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"Now two Republican-controlled House committees are investigating the solicitations .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Dan Mendelson of the health care consulting group Avalere says","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that makes donors skittish .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"`` Much as a health care company might really want to improve enrollment ,","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"they also need to make sure","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"that they do not run afoul of politicians on either side of the aisle , ''","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"Mendelson says .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"If health care companies hold back ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"he says ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"it 's going to be much harder to reach all of those people in all of those communities .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"`` The fact of the matter is that","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"if you starve a media campaign for funding ,","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"you 're not going to have the reach","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"that you otherwise would ,","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"and that 's the situation","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"that we find ourselves in , ''","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"he says .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"There 's another key part of this campaign :","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"Sicker and older people without insurance may be eager to sign up Oct. 1 .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"to make the system work financially ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"young and healthy people","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"who do n't need much medical care","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"have to get into the pool , too .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"So you can expect administration officials around the country to give lots more commencement speeches this season ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"telling captive audiences of 20-somethings :","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Congratulations on your diploma .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Now make sure to sign up for health coverage in the fall .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":225,"left":114,"right":224,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":114,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":224,"left":119,"right":223,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":116,"right":118,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":116,"left":115,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":117,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":154,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":124,"right":153,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":8,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":120,"right":122,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":11,"right":121,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":150,"right":152,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":133,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":127,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":14,"right":126,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":129,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":128,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity"